,"msg":"錯2樣野<br />\n第一樣一面巴打講左<br />\n第二樣係equal係== 唔係="},{"pid":"fdad3ed6b5592efdf0be2537941f5cb80c3078b3","tid":461712,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"同埋改返好啲indentation"},{"pid":"8845f585307d7ca438b51f53d413dda7b1b22a28","tid":461712,"uid":46548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:24:06.000Z","msg":"counter i 喺返個loop入面declare"},{"pid":"486feba453081fa5db807978ed5e91a1bdfce59c","tid":461712,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"搞掂咗啦 感謝各位大愛巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身唔知strlen係指尾嗰個char咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e32f2577a03c80ca5de28c481c45689f0eb9ee4","tid":461712,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>counter i 喺返個loop入面declare</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放喺嗰for loop到？ 但係佢會話我未declare"},{"pid":"1b00fe3d0122d3e9b413050f0c70a845563350d5","tid":461712,"uid":143105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搞掂咗啦 感謝各位大愛巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身唔知strlen係指尾嗰個char咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔啱<br />\nstrlen 指你條string既長度<br />\narr[strlen(arr) -1] 先係尾嗰個char, 因為條array由0開始計<br />\n而 arr[strlen(arr)] 係拍EOS亦即係'\\0'"},{"pid":"6d6460fcaf642eb39b8202f7a18aa1372fe95bbb","tid":461712,"uid":143105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>counter i 喺返個loop入面declare</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放喺嗰for loop到？ 但係佢會話我未declare</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下<br />\nfor(int i=0; arr[i] != '\\0'; i++)"},{"pid":"7905e4f886cd04f9e016b79e748ea8881688c959","tid":461712,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搞掂咗啦 感謝各位大愛巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身唔知strlen係指尾嗰個char咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔啱<br />\nstrlen 指你條string既長度<br />\narr[strlen(arr) -1] 先係尾嗰個char, 因為條array由0開始計<br />\n而 arr[strlen(arr)] 係拍EOS亦即係'\\0'</blockquote><br />\n感謝清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfa235a2eb2bd66f50b20f5fe2e603743f0a320","tid":461712,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>counter i 喺返個loop入面declare</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放喺嗰for loop到？ 但係佢會話我未declare</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下<br />\nfor(int i=0; arr[i] != '\\0'; i++)</blockquote><br />\nrun唔到 佢話only allowed in C99 or C11 mode"},{"pid":"d0e434ef540d7bde9968cf163f0bf70b51b199df","tid":461712,"uid":46548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>counter i 喺返個loop入面declare</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放喺嗰for loop到？ 但係佢會話我未declare</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下<br />\nfor(int i=0; arr[i] != '\\0'; i++)</blockquote><br />\nrun唔到 佢話only allowed in C99 or C11 mode</blockquote><br />\n因為你連自己寫緊c定c++都唔知"},{"pid":"b3fae3845f7f703ea98633d13401163657488fe2","tid":461712,"uid":46548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>counter i 喺返個loop入面declare</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放喺嗰for loop到？ 但係佢會話我未declare</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下<br />\nfor(int i=0; arr[i] != '\\0'; i++)</blockquote><br />\nrun唔到 佢話only allowed in C99 or C11 mode</blockquote><br />\n因為你連自己寫緊c定c++都唔知</blockquote><br />\n擺落個loop入面declare會令到i唔可以喺loop以外既範圍用 純粹係一個好既習慣<br />\n<br />\n至於出error 係因為你用c run緊個program 而舊版本既c係唔support你係個loop入面先declare 新啲既c或者c++就ok<br />\nc++既file extension係.cpp<br />\nc就係.c<br />\n<br />\n最後屌多句 學寫code多啲善用google<br />\n你google段error 其實已經揾到你想要既答案"},{"pid":"8e1258cd51189d795258d1d2c940cc8c7393903b","tid":461712,"uid":55420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"agger樓上位巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我啲programming assignment成日都係靠google/stack overflow學點做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}